mod.name: Stick War 143675
mod.description:
Tired of mods being too hard? Let us then recommend this groundbreaking secret technique: Practice!
Practice is good and fun for everyone! Fight a whole ass army and a boss in 143675 milliseconds while your screen has a seizure, control mercy being on RNJesus, and your army gets reset when you destroy the statue! It's good fun if you practice it!
Have you been spamming swords since 2009? Try Stick_War_143675.swf! It's very good, we promise!
'Best mod ever!' -Medusa (real)
'Dogshit. 0/10. I'm outta here.' -s07 (probably)
